   10. DATA COLLECTION & USAGE

     All data entered by the User does NOT get saved until the remember me login is used. Then the data listed below will get 
     saved to automatically log-in next time.Everything else, Guild data, Jobs, Profile data come       
     from the FFXVI API (Unofficial) through the App providing your ID, Server and Name. The App does NOT connect to another server 
     besides the API,so no data gets stored on another server. This data is needed to provide the service.


